@RestController : define a controller class where every method automatically returns a JSON (or XML) response instead of a view
@RequestMapping("brands") : used to map HTTP requests to controller methods (or classes)
1. Autowired function save from BrandServices
--Logic of function
2. Handle HTTP Post request : @RequestMapping(method = RequestMethod.POST)
3. Handle HTTP Response : ResponseEntity<?> create(@RequestBody BrandDTO brandDTO)
4. Convert DTO to Entity : Brand brand = Mapper.toBrand(brandDTO);
5. Save Entity
6. Return HTTP Response : return ResponseEntity.ok(brand);
